{"tid":1605291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普擬將限制美國投資流入中國市場？外交部迴應","createTime":"2019-09-30T08:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:06:40.000Z","uid":26367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6867c15b7b40cb81ba717f0ab2ceb57e98cbbfb5","tid":1605291,"uid":26367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:49:49.000Z","msg":"耿爽指出，我們注意到了相關報道，也注意到了美國財政部發言人做出的迴應。<br />\n<br />\n中美經貿合作以及中美財經合作的本質是互利共贏的，搞極限施壓，甚至企圖強行地將中美關係脱鈎，勢必損害中美兩國企業和民眾利益，引發金融市場動盪，進而危及國際貿易和世界經濟的增長。這不符合國際社會的共同利益。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽表示，我們希望美方能夠同中方共同努力，來不斷深化兩國之間的經貿合作與財經合作，同時也希望美方能同中方相向而行，本着建設性的態度來尋找解決問題的辦法。"},{"pid":"1856888d5bb7274cdafb0a54dd3f9f2f3292ddaf","tid":1605291,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:51:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2863b154cf91377a03183d996d91438589ef4c7a","tid":1605291,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"食到浸屎味嗎 爽爽"},{"pid":"3af2fa260e153bd018d9daa1b48da5c457943d9e","tid":1605291,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"唔知點解一見到耿爽個名就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ed531696de6c111238de034f77ef1b99332545","tid":1605291,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"今次咁客氣"},{"pid":"4bd032fbee34d359b08f2c0912e54768f7a87f3a","tid":1605291,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"Gif 呢喂"},{"pid":"508f741cf83da04c2ccd9c2fb6866aa295061da6","tid":1605291,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:05:35.000Z","msg":"侵侵做對了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e747131f94e07e0e0231c2cbab2afd6c0bae46ad","tid":1605291,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"點解今次唔強力繾責<img src=\"/assets/fac